statements: SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics;
SELECT user_id, created_at FROM voice_biometrics;
SELECT voice_profile FROM voice_biometrics WHERE user_id='123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics WHERE created_at >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, voice_profile, created_at FROM voice_biometrics ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT user_id, voice_profile FROM voice_biometrics ORDER BY user_id DESC, created_at ASC;
SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000' AND created_at > '2021-01-01 00:00:00' ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT user_id, voice_profile FROM voice_biometrics WHERE created_at BETWEEN '2021-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2021-12-31 23:59:59' ORDER BY created_at ASC;
SELECT user_id, voice_profile, created_at FROM voice_biometrics WHERE user_id IN ('123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000', '321e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001') ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM voice_biometrics WHERE created_at < '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT voice_recording_path, recording_date FROM voice_biometrics_data WHERE user_id = 2;
SELECT user_id, voice_data FROM voice_biometrics_data ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT login_time, logout_time FROM authentication_logs WHERE user_id = 3;
SELECT user_id, voice_data, recording_date FROM voice_biometrics_data WHERE recording_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT voice_data, recording_date FROM voice_biometrics_data ORDER BY recording_date DESC;
SELECT vb.user_id, COUNT(al.log_id) AS total_logins FROM voice_biometrics_data vb LEFT JOIN authentication_logs al ON vb.user_id = al.user_id GROUP BY vb.user_id HAVING total_logins > 10;
SELECT * FROM authentication_logs WHERE user_id = 2 AND logout_time IS NOT NULL ORDER BY logout_time ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT DISTINCT vb.user_id, vb.recording_date, al.login_time FROM voice_biometrics_data vb INNER JOIN authentication_logs al ON vb.user_id = al.user_id WHERE vb.recording_date > '2022-01-01' AND al.login_time < '2022-03-01';
SELECT * FROM support_agents;
SELECT name, department FROM support_agents WHERE department = 'Customer Support';
SELECT caller_id, timestamp FROM verification_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT name, department FROM support_agents WHERE name LIKE 'J%';
SELECT * FROM voice_authentication ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT * FROM voice_authentication WHERE id = 100;
SELECT caller_id, timestamp FROM voice_authentication WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, caller_id, timestamp FROM voice_authentication WHERE caller_id LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM support_agents WHERE department = 'Customer Support';
SELECT caller_id, result FROM verification_logs WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics_data ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT user_id, sample_date FROM voice_biometrics_data WHERE sample_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT call_id, user_id FROM support_calls WHERE call_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT call_id, call_duration FROM support_calls WHERE call_duration > 300;
SELECT * FROM call_transcripts ORDER BY transcript_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM voice_biometrics_data ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, sample_date FROM voice_biometrics_data WHERE sample_date >= '2022-01-01' AND sample_date <= '2022-12-31' ORDER BY sample_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, call_date, call_duration FROM support_calls WHERE call_duration > 60 ORDER BY call_date DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT u.user_id, u.voice_auth_enabled, c.call_date FROM user_profiles u JOIN support_calls c ON u.user_id = c.user_id WHERE u.voice_auth_enabled = true ORDER BY c.call_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT t.transcript_text FROM call_transcripts t JOIN support_calls c ON t.call_id = c.call_id WHERE c.call_date >= '2022-03-01' ORDER BY c.call_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM voice_users;
SELECT username, voice_template FROM voice_users WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT auth_id, voice_sample, authentication_result FROM voice_authentication WHERE authentication_result = TRUE;
SELECT caller_id, callee_id, call_duration FROM voice_call_logs ORDER BY call_timestamp DESC;
SELECT agent_name, department FROM voice_support_agents WHERE department = 'Customer Support';
SELECT * FROM voice_users WHERE username = 'Alice';
SELECT user_id, username FROM voice_users ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT agent_id, agent_name, department FROM voice_support_agents WHERE department = 'Customer Support' ORDER BY agent_name DESC;
SELECT call_id, caller_id, callee_id FROM voice_call_logs WHERE call_timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY call_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, authentication_result FROM voice_authentication WHERE authentication_result = true AND user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
